	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=96464><span id= >EllessarBardofBB</span></a><br><span id=notbold>10 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.50]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Even with a 25/25 weapon, bards do not match the melee damage of a paladin/SK wielding a 25/25... (double attack &gt; dual wield, and has the primary hand damage bonus)... without talking about bashing.&nbsp;&nbsp;Bards (even with this) are still well behind other melee classes.  <br><br>So, I would not think this is a mistake, rather the bard melee issues are an oversight by Verant that is now being fixed with weapons like this.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu May  9 11:41:38 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
